-- BG says to buy Connecticut power plant
-- 
-- Thu Dec 28, 2006 3:14am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/12/28/businesspro-bg-lake-road-dc-idUSWLA710120061228

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - British gas producer BG Group Plc ( BG.L ) 
said on Thursday it had agreed to buy the Lake Road power plant 
in Connecticut, United States, for $685 million. 

  BG said it expected the purchase of the 805 megawatt gas 
and oil fired plant to complete in the first quarter of next 
year, following U.S. regulatory approvals.